    "iniNotFound": {
      "title": "*.ini files couldn't be loaded.",
      "text": [
        "<p>Are the *.ini files missing? Let's troubleshoot:</p>",
        "<ul>",
        "<li><b>Start the game first.</b> It will create the missing *.ini files.</li>",
        "<li>Check if *.ini files exist in <code>C:\\Users\\[your username]\\Documents\\My Games\\Fallout 76\\</code>. They should be called <code>Fallout76.ini</code> and <code>Fallout76Prefs.ini</code> or <code>Project76.ini</code> and <code>Project76Prefs.ini</code>.</li>",
        "<li>Check your <a>profile settings</a>, especially the advanced section. Are the *.ini path and prefix set to the correct values?</li>",
        "</ul>"
      ],
      "createIniButton": "Create ini files from included template"
    },
    "iniParseError": {
      "title": "An *.ini file contains invalid syntax and couldn't be parsed.",
      "text": [
        "<p>Are the ini files corrupted? Have they been edited? Try one of these options:</p>",
        "<ul>",
        "<li>Open the displayed ini file and fix the error if you know how to do it, or</li>",
        "<li><b>Start the game</b> and change a few settings, or</li>",
        "<li>Delete the *.ini files in the folder <code>C:\\Users\\[your username]\\Documents\\My Games\\Fallout 76\\</code> and then <b>start the game</b>. This will reset all settings to their defaults.</li>",
        "</ul>"
      ]
    },
